  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the correlation between clinical and ultrasound findings in children presented
      with signs suggestive of bronchiolitis and to validate an ultrasound score for bronchiolitis
      that will correlate with specific clinical outcomes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
